ProtoTheorem:
. "A function $f$ is continuous at $\widehat u$ if and only if
   $$ \lim_{n\to\infty} f(u_n)=f(\widehat u) $$ whenever 
   $\{u_n\}$ is a sequence in $D_f$ that converges to $\widehat
   u$."
